replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:51:20.000Z","msg":"教協應該都要百屌成才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋你提出既要求都可以係遊行/集會既主題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行出黎可以凝聚到呢個界別聲音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你可以係email template到加返呢項意見再send比教協同葉建源"},{"pid":"56c54fccfb666694ad0ea0b2da996385ac0d7bed","tid":1741241,"uid":9163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70fb895841a26f9adb01d1eefccecf6446dd02ef","tid":1741241,"uid":331861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:46:44.000Z","msg":"唔好呼籲組織遊行/集會 即接<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要求向政府申請全港再罷課仲實際啦</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n交通塞到咁，仲周圍d學生返學放學都被捉，咁都要d學生返學?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:56:21.000Z","msg":"封信好似無講要學生返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f2da9fe248044a4c9547ef96f9af2b3688d8ad3","tid":1741241,"uid":77431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94b8c8e6d99ae5366fd65030492f5a101862d6cf","tid":1741241,"uid":86833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:45:25.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，蒙唔蒙面先<br />\n<br />\n驚畀人清算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:57:40.000Z","msg":"我諗如果教協真係會搞集會/遊行，佢地到時都會有相關建議<br />\n但現階段最緊要反映我地想教協作為so-called工會要做返多啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7243e90e75dff4f84829bce9203b2676ff4c1063","tid":1741241,"uid":255952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:59:00.000Z","msg":"817教協遊行上禮賓府，幾千人比狗封剩一條馬路行，<br />\n成班教畜係到大叫「唔該啊sir開路」，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開返條路少少就成班講晒「多謝」「唔該啊sir」「辛苦晒」。<br />\n仲有果日既口號係叫啲咩：<br />\n「學生加油！」「家長加油！」「老師加油！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遊多次，咪玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3308c4bd52eff9cd508426ddda73539f42cd9b5e","tid":1741241,"uid":9163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7243e90e75dff4f84829bce9203b2676ff4c1063","tid":1741241,"uid":255952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:59:00.000Z","msg":"817教協遊行上禮賓府，幾千人比狗封剩一條馬路行，<br />\n成班教畜係到大叫「唔該啊sir開路」，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開返條路少少就成班講晒「多謝」「唔該啊sir」「辛苦晒」。<br />\n仲有果日既口號係叫啲咩：<br />\n「學生加油！」「家長加油！」「老師加油！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遊多次，咪玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T13:01:53.000Z","msg":"咁做教育呢行係有啲加鎖既<br />\n唔通叫成班老師大叫 屌你老母 黑警咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f76395edc2717c3f481b26576fabcda01908361d","tid":1741241,"uid":256128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T13:02:35.000Z","msg":"P牌幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8c5f08c499b9363f6af1ce7e6b4a09e05dc81f7","tid":1741241,"uid":9163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f76395edc2717c3f481b26576fabcda01908361d","tid":1741241,"uid":256128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T13:02:35.000Z","msg":"P牌幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTim